data.description: Welcome to this updated 3 Bedroom, 2 Bath home featuring granite counter tops, a breakfast bar, and stainless-steel appliances in this unique kitchen.  The extra cabinetry and countertop extend from the kitchen into the dining room and provide ample storage and plenty of space for all your little extras. The beautiful tile and vinyl plank flooring throughout the home demands easy maintenance.  The updated bathrooms offer a modern look and fresh feel. Enjoy the outdoors on the covered porch or relax in the covered carport. The oversize driveway provides plenty of parking space. And don't forget about the large, fenced backyard, perfect for entertaining or letting your furry friends roam freely. Don't miss out on this gem, give us a call today for your private viewing.
